{% if enable_browser -%}
| `session: health` | Analyze browser sessions for stale tabs |
{% endif -%}
{% if notes_app != 'none' -%}
| `stale:` | Find dormant projects, aging drafts |
{% endif -%}
| `batch: weekly-reflection` | Run qualitative reflection workflow |
| `batch: [workflow]` | Trigger any batch workflow |

### Proactive Alerts
When running batch processes, surface:
- Stated intentions without follow-through
- Contradictions across sources
- Dormant projects / neglected relationships
- Pattern convergences (same topic in 3+ sources)

